      "description": "This F87 M2 is a driver-focused example featuring the N55 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six and a rare 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical vitals are strong, with the Active M Differential providing precise torque distribution and the factory-spec suspension maintaining its original damping characteristics. It sits on staggered forged wheels with plenty of tread remaining on the Michelin rubber. While it shows the expected patina of a well-loved performance car, the engine pulls cleanly through the rev range with no signs of heat soak or turbo lag. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and a high-performance brake fluid flush, making it track-ready or a spirited daily driver.",
